comments: Theis (BOS) brushes Fultz's (ORL) arm and doesn't affect his driving shot attempt.
Ross (ORL) makes incidental contact as he legally contests Theis' (BOS) shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) moves into Fultz's (ORL) body off-ball and affects his FOM.
Theis (BOS) establishes legal position in Augustin's (ORL) path during the pick and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Fultz (ORL) makes marginal contact by brushing Theis' (BOS) shoulder as both players make natural movements toward the rebound.
Tatum (BOS) maintains legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Vucevic (ORL).
Theis (BOS) establishes legal position in Ross' (ORL) path during the screen and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Tatum (BOS) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two legal steps prior to entering his upward shooting motion.
Theis (BOS) collapses his hand as he absorbs the body contact from Augustin (ORL) during his driving shot attempt.
Fultz (ORL) makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) on the perimeter and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Tatum (BOS) has a legal bent forearm to Fultz's (ORL) body that he does not extend during his drive.
Tatum (BOS) cleanly blocks Ross' (ORL) shot prior to making incidental contact.
Clark (ORL) dislodges the loose ball from Theis (BOS) prior to making incidental contact with his arm.
Fultz (ORL) initiates and delivers contact by lowering his arm into Tatum's (BOS) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes legal position in Tatum's (BOS) path during the pick and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Theis (BOS) makes marginal contact with Fultz (ORL) and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Theis (BOS) turns and delivers body contact that affects Clark's (ORL) driving shot attempt.
Futlz (ORL) legally contest Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes legal position in Hayward's (BOS) path during the pick and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Theis (BOS) maintains legal guarding position as he cleanly blocks Ross' (ORL) driving shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) fumbles the ball in transition. He then regains control by gathering the ball on his left foot and taking one legal step prior to his pass.
Vucevic (ORL) makes marginal contact with Theis (BOS) during rebounding.
Vucevic (ORL) maintains legal guarding position during Smart's (BOS) drive.
Hayward (BOS) is already in Frazier's (ORL) path and makes some contact as they disengage.
Hayward (BOS) establishes legal position in Fultz' (ORL) path during the screen and does not deliver contact.
Theis (BOS) establishes legal position in Fultz's (ORL) path during the screen and does not deliver contact.
Theis (BOS) is established in Ennis III's (ORL) path and makes marginal contact as he releases to roll toward the basket.
Fultz (ORL) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two legal steps as he comes to a stop.
Theis (BOS) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Vucevic (ORL) after the releases his jump shot attempt.
